Description: Add a new Claim and attach a file to it after it has been created.
Click on a specific Claim to display its contents.
Download a file attached to a specific Claim.
Search for a Claim entering valid/existing data to search and display a specific Claim.

Search for a Claim using invalid/unexisting data.
No specific Claim should be found.

Upload a file and select the "Medical Records" file name option.
Uploaded file will be displayed as "Medical Records".

Upload a file and select the "Other" file name option.
Uploaded file will be displayed with the same file name.
